adventurers-outpost.name: Meet Favorite Disney Pals at Adventurers Outpost
adventurers-outpost.sort_name: meet favorite disney pals at adventurers outpost
adventurers-outpost.summary: Halt your adventuring to enjoy a magical meet ‘n’ greet with Mickey and Minnie at their exploration headquarters.

up-great-bird-adventure.name: UP! A Great Bird Adventure
up-great-bird-adventure.summary: Discover some of the world’s most exotic birds during an all-new show starring those fun-loving pals from Disney•Pixar’s Up!

dj-anaan.name: DJ Anaan
dj-anaan.summary: Street party in Asia that features a DJ spinning hot international tunes.

tree-of-life-nighttime-awakenings.name: Tree of Life Awakenings
tree-of-life-nighttime-awakenings.what_it_is: Nighttime light and film show projected on to the Tree of Life
tree-of-life-nighttime-awakenings.ultimate_task: See one showing of The Awakening

harambe-acrobats.name: Harambe Village Acrobats
harambe-acrobats.summary: These performers tumble, drum, dance, and make themselves into pyramids for the amusement of the gathering crowd.

dinosaur.name: DINOSAUR
dinosaur.average_wait_assumes: Full capacity operation with 18-second dispatch interval.
dinosaur.summary: Take off on a scary, prehistoric tour aboard a rip-roaring Time Rover to save a dinosaur from extinction.

navi-river-journey.name: Na'vi River Journey
navi-river-journey.when_to_go: Before 9:30 a.m., during the last 2 hours before closing, or use FastPass+
navi-river-journey.summary: Delight in the pageantry and puppetry of this big-as-Broadway show celebrating Simba, the lion cub who would be king!

gorilla-falls-exploration-trail.name: Gorilla Falls Exploration Trail
gorilla-falls-exploration-trail.ultimate_task: Travel full trail. Take photo in gorilla area and with 1 other animal.
gorilla-falls-exploration-trail.summary: Explore a lush tropical forest inhabited by native African wildlife including gorillas, hippos and exotic birds.

maharajah-jungle-trek.name: Maharajah Jungle Trek
maharajah-jungle-trek.ultimate_task: Travel full trail. Take photo in tiger area and with 1 other animal.
maharajah-jungle-trek.summary: Embark on a self-guided walking tour of Southeast Asia—home to tigers, dozens of bird species, a flying fox and a Komodo dragon.

wilderness-explorers.name: Wilderness Explorers
wilderness-explorers.when_to_go: Sign up first thing in the morning and complete activities throughout the day.
wilderness-explorers.summary: Become a Wilderness Explorer—complete challenges and earn adventure badges as you work your way around the Park.

habitat-habit.name: Habitat Habit!
habitat-habit.ultimate_task: Take photo with animal or display.
habitat-habit.summary: See cotton-top tamarin monkeys and learn how you can share your world with animals at this outdoor discovery trail.

conservation-station.name: Conservation Station
conservation-station.ultimate_task: Listen to full Song of the Rainforest audio. And for 10 minutes total explore the other exhibits, surgeries, and animals here.
conservation-station.summary: Explore a wildlife conservation center home to animal encounters, interactive exhibits and a veterinary facility.

expedition-everest.name: Expedition Everest - Legend of the Forbidden Mountain
expedition-everest.what_it_is: High-speed, outdoor roller coaster through Nepalese mountain village
expedition-everest.when_to_go: Before 9:30 a.m., or after 3 p.m., or use FastPass+.
expedition-everest.sort_name: expedition everest legend of the forbidden mountain
expedition-everest.summary: Careen through the Himalayan mountains on a speeding train while avoiding the clutches of the mythic Abominable Snowman.

discovery-island-trails.name: Discovery Island Trails
discovery-island-trails.ultimate_task: Travel a trail and take photo adjacent to Tree of Life carved animal. (No photos from a distance.)
discovery-island-trails.summary: Stroll along tranquil pathways around the Tree of Life and discover a lush landscape brimming with wildlife.

finding-nemo-the-musical.name: Finding Nemo - The Musical
finding-nemo-the-musical.what_it_is: Enclosed venue for live stage shows
finding-nemo-the-musical.summary: Based on the hit animated movie, this must-“sea” adventure makes a splash with spectacular music and stunning theatrical puppetry.

avatar-flight-of-passage.name: Avatar Flight of Passage
avatar-flight-of-passage.when_to_go: As soon as the park opens, or use FastPass+
avatar-flight-of-passage.summary: Fly on the back of a mountain banshee during an exhilarating, 3D ride above this vast moon, only at Pandora – The World of Avatar.

tam-tam-congo.name: Tam Tam Drummers of Harambe
tam-tam-congo.summary: Dance to the rapturous beat of the Congo as these vibrant African drummers deliver driving rhythms.

rivers-of-light.name: Rivers of Light
rivers-of-light.summary: Embrace the magic of nature during a nighttime scene awash with captivating special effects, music and animal folklore.

tough-to-be-a-bug.name: It's Tough to Be a Bug!
tough-to-be-a-bug.short_name: It's Tough to Be a Bug
tough-to-be-a-bug.sort_name: its tough to be a bug
tough-to-be-a-bug.summary: Discover what it’s like to be a bug during this 3D film and live show inspired by the Disney•Pixar film A Bug’s Life.

wildlife-express-train-africa-station.name: Wildlife Express Train: Africa Station
wildlife-express-train-africa-station.what_it_is: Scenic railroad ride to Rafiki's Planet Watch and Conservation Station
wildlife-express-train-africa-station.ultimate_task: Ride to and from Rafiki's Planet Watch.
wildlife-express-train-africa-station.summary: Ride the rails on this rustic locomotive that travels behind-the-scenes from Harambe, Africa to Rafiki’s Planet Watch.

karibu-sisters.name: Karibu Sisters
karibu-sisters.summary: The sirens of Harambe, the Karibu Sisters are three lovely ladies that entertain with storytelling and a cappella music as they sell their wares.

viva-gaia-street-band.name: Viva Gaia Street Band
viva-gaia-street-band.summary: Transport to a never-to-be-forgotten celebration of life where you can enjoy a multi-cultural troupe leading a Caribbean street party. It’s a fiery mix of melody and masquerade—complete with magnificent colors, costumes, rhythm and dance!

divine.name: Divine
divine.summary: Bedecked in foliage and luxuriant vines, she blends so completely with Animal Kingdom’s dense flora that you don’t notice her until she moves.

swotu-waya-navi-drum-ceremony.name: Pandora Drummers – Swotu Wayä
swotu-waya-navi-drum-ceremony.summary: Explore the unique sounds and organic rhythms beating forth from “the sacred place of song,” only at Pandora – The World of Avatar.

boneyard.name: The Boneyard
boneyard.ultimate_task: Take photo in Jeep or ride a slide. Also take photo with exposed bone at Mammoth Dig Site.
boneyard.summary: An open air play space designed to look like a dinosaur dig site where kids can explore and have fun.

wildlife-express-train-rafikis-planet-wa.name: Wildlife Express Train: Rafiki's Planet Watch Station
wildlife-express-train-rafikis-planet-wa.what_it_is: Scenic railroad ride to Rafiki's Planet Watch and Conservation Station
wildlife-express-train-rafikis-planet-wa.ultimate_task: Ride to and from Rafiki's Planet Watch.
wildlife-express-train-rafikis-planet-wa.sort_name: wildlife express train rafikis planet watch station
wildlife-express-train-rafikis-planet-wa.summary: Ride the rails on this rustic locomotive that travels behind-the-scenes from Harambe, Rafiki’s Planet Watch to Africa.

winged-encounters-kingdom-takes-flight.name: Winged Encounters - The Kingdom Takes Flight
winged-encounters-kingdom-takes-flight.sort_name: winged encounters the kingdom takes flight

wildlife-parti.name: Harambe Wildlife Parti
wildlife-parti.summary: The Wildlife Parti will bring the African village of Harambe to life with a street party and bustling marketplace.

kali-river-rapids.name: Kali River Rapids
kali-river-rapids.when_to_go: First or last hour the park is open, or use FastPass+ or the single-rider line
kali-river-rapids.summary: Set out on a rip-roaring, river raft ride through a lush jungle landscape ravaged by illegal logging.

animal-encounters-up-close-interactions.name: Animal Encounters: Up-Close Interactions
animal-encounters-up-close-interactions.summary: Show that exposes guests to live animals.

triceratop-spin.name: TriceraTop Spin
triceratop-spin.summary: Fly high on a dinosaur around a twirling tin-toy top at this delightful carnival-inspired attraction.

festival-of-the-lion-king.name: Festival of the Lion King
festival-of-the-lion-king.summary: Delight in the pageantry and puppetry of this big-as-Broadway show celebrating Simba, the lion cub who would be king!

affection-section.name: Affection Section
affection-section.summary: Enjoy friendly, hands-on encounters with a variety of animals, including goats and sheep, at this open-air petting zoo.

primeval-whirl.name: Primeval Whirl
primeval-whirl.when_to_go: During the first 2 hours the park is open, in the hour before park closing
primeval-whirl.summary: Spin and slide on a time-machine coaster back to the dinosaur age through a madcap maze of curves and drops.

discovery-island-carnivale.name: Discovery Island Carnivale
discovery-island-carnivale.summary: Join a cavalcade of dancers, stilt walkers and musicians for a nighttime dance party in the streets of Discovery Island!

valley-of-moara.name: Valley of Mo'ara
valley-of-moara.ultimate_task: Enjoy for 10 minutes. Take 3 unique photos.
valley-of-moara.summary: Pandora’s best feature is its environment, and the Valley of Mo'ara is the most scenic section of Pandora: The World of Avatar.

kilimanjaro-safaris.name: Kilimanjaro Safaris
kilimanjaro-safaris.what_it_is: Truck ride through an African wildlife reservation
kilimanjaro-safaris.when_to_go: As soon as the park opens or in the 2 hours before closing, or use FastPass+
kilimanjaro-safaris.summary: Ride off in an open-air vehicle for a day or evening tour of a lush African savanna, home to real-live exotic animals.
